how to debug anuglar applications?

1) open developer tools --- f12

2)	open debugger tab

3) expand our js files

4) put a break point where we need to have control.

	next line -- f10
	to go into a method -- f11.
	to come out from a method -- shift + f11
	to go to next break point -- f8


verifying the id presense in the db.














